ActFirst Nations Goods and Services Tax Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the First Nations Goods and Services Tax Act, No. 2016-2 (Cayoose Creek)
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULE 1 TO THE FIRST NATIONS GOODS AND SERVICES TAX ACT, No. 2016-2 (CAYOOSE CREEK) in order to add (1) the name of Cayoose Creek, (2) the name of its governing body and (3) the description of its reserves where its First Nations goods and services tax law could apply.
